name: Yellow Specs
description:
Classic Wayfarer style with the Blue Bird logo down the arm. The Specs are made with Rubberized Plastic so they are able take a Roundhouse kick to the face. Whether you are taking these to the beach, or out for a night on the town; these Specs are built to please.

Dimensions: 5.75in. (front), 2in. (tall), 5.25in. (arms)
Rubberized finish
UV400 protection
Impact resistant lenses
